   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    FUNNY:
    <br/>
    The sign "funny" just uses one hand and is done near the nose and/or brushes off 
the nose twice.
    <br/>
    (You don't actually have to touch the nose.)
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <img border="0" height="239" src="../../signjpegs/f/funnya1.jpg" width="236"/>
    <img border="0" height="239" src="../../signjpegs/f/funnya2.jpg" width="236"/>
