    <img border="0" height="239" src="../../signjpegs/f/funnya5.jpg" width="236"/>
    <img border="0" height="239" src="../../signjpegs/f/funnya6.jpg" width="236"/>
    <br/>
   </p>
   <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    To make light of.  /  To 
make fun of:
    <br/>
    The right hand comes off the nose and thwacks the left hand and then the left 
hand moves up and comes down and thwacks the right hand.  (This is sort of 
a rare/weird sign. You are better off just using the sign "TEASE" or the sign 
MOCK.)
    <br/>
